---
/**
 * Solutions — section "approche éditoriale" mood "cream".
 *
 * Stationed right after the dark hero, painted in the cream paper tone the
 * mountain ridge transitioned into. A soft warm radial orb floats behind
 * the right column to echo the Websenso "Solutions" rhythm. Body copy is
 * editorial: long sentence with strategically-bolded keywords and a
 * gradient-mark on the most important phrase.
 *
 * Anchor: #approche
 */
---

<section
	id="services"
	class="solutions section-cream-orb section-pad"
	data-section-mood="cream"
	style="--orb-x: 88%; --orb-y: 30%;"
	aria-labelledby="solutions-title"
>
	<div class="solutions__inner">
		<header class="solutions__head">
			<p class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="eyebrow-prefix" aria-hidden="true">[ 01 ]</span> Notre approche</p>
			<h2
				id="solutions-title"
				class="solutions__title h-1 reveal balance"
				style="--delay:.1s"
			>
				Une <span class="mark-gradient">agence créative</span>
				à taille humaine.<br />
				Pas un studio générique. Pas une usine à templates.
			</h2>
		</header>

		<div class="solutions__body reveal" style="--delay:.25s">
			<p>
				Chez <strong>ID&nbsp;Skillz</strong>, chaque projet commence par une
				<strong>conversation</strong>, pas par un devis. Nous prenons le temps de
				comprendre votre marque, vos clients, vos ambitions — puis nous composons
				<em>l&rsquo;équipe juste</em>&nbsp;: développeurs, designers, vidéastes,
				modeleurs 3D selon le besoin réel.
			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Quatre métiers</strong> réunis sous une seule direction artistique,
				pour vous éviter cinq prestataires différents qui se renvoient la balle.
				Vous gardez un interlocuteur, une vision, un livrable cohérent. Du brief
				à la mise en ligne, et au-delà.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="solutions__cta reveal" style="--delay:.4s">
			<a class="solutions__link" href="#methode">
				<span>Voir notre méthode</span>
				<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
					<path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" />
				</svg>
			</a>
			<span class="solutions__divider" aria-hidden="true"></span>
			<a class="solutions__link" href="#expertises">
				<span>Voir les expertises</span>
				<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
					<path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" />
				</svg>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Marker glyph echoing the hero sketch, hand-drawn vibe -->
	<svg
		class="solutions__glyph"
		viewBox="0 0 200 200"
		fill="none"
		stroke="currentColor"
		stroke-width="1.25"
		stroke-linecap="round"
		stroke-linejoin="round"
		aria-hidden="true"
	>
		<!-- Open quote glyph, sketched -->
		<path d="M40 90 Q 30 80 30 60 Q 30 40 50 30" />
		<path d="M58 90 Q 78 110 78 140" />
		<path d="M120 90 Q 110 80 110 60 Q 110 40 130 30" />
		<path d="M138 90 Q 158 110 158 140" />
	</svg>

	<!-- Soft hairline transitioning into next section. -->
	<div class="solutions__hairline" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>

<style>
	.solutions {
		position: relative;
		isolation: isolate;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	/* Cream orb parallax. The base `section-cream-orb` utility paints the
	 * radial gradient at --orb-x/--orb-y; we override those vars via JS or
	 * scroll-tied CSS. Currently we animate the orb's translate on a slow
	 * loop to mimic the breathing blob behind the Websenso solutions H1
	 * (00:04). On reduced-motion the orb stays static. */
	.solutions::after {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: -1;
		background: radial-gradient(
			circle at var(--solutions-orb-x, 85%) var(--solutions-orb-y, 38%),
			color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent-cool) 16%, transparent) 0%,
			color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent-cool) 6%, transparent) 28%,
			transparent 55%
		);
		filter: blur(40px);
		animation: solutionsOrbBreathe 14s ease-in-out infinite;
	}
	@keyframes solutionsOrbBreathe {
		0%, 100% { --solutions-orb-x: 85%; --solutions-orb-y: 38%; transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
		50%      { --solutions-orb-x: 78%; --solutions-orb-y: 46%; transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.85; }
	}
	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.solutions::after { animation: none; }
	}

	.solutions__inner {
		position: relative;
		width: var(--container-narrow);
		margin-inline: auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
		gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
		max-width: 60rem;
	}

	.solutions__head {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.solutions__title {
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #0A0908;
	}
	.solutions__title .mark-gradient {
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.solutions__body {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		max-width: 50rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.05vw + 0.7rem, 1.35rem);
		line-height: 1.55;
		color: #2A2520;
		font-weight: 300;
	}
	.solutions__body strong {
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #0A0908;
		position: relative;
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0 0.15em;
		background-image: linear-gradient(
			180deg,
			transparent 60%,
			color-mix(in oklab, var(--color-sienne) 18%, transparent) 60%
		);
		background-repeat: no-repeat;
		background-size: 0% 100%;
		transition: background-size 0.9s var(--ease-emphatic);
	}
	.solutions__body.is-visible strong {
		background-size: 100% 100%;
		transition-delay: calc(var(--si, 0) * 80ms + 200ms);
	}
	/* On hover of a strong keyword we shift to the cool accent for a
	 * micro-interaction that announces the new color system. */
	.solutions__body strong:hover {
		background-image: linear-gradient(
			180deg,
			transparent 60%,
			color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent-cool) 22%, transparent) 60%
		);
	}
	.solutions__body em {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--accent-cool);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.solutions__cta {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}
	.solutions__link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding: 0.7rem 1.1rem 0.7rem 0;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #0A0908;
		border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
		transition:
			gap 0.3s var(--ease-emphatic),
			color 0.2s var(--ease-soft);
	}
	.solutions__link svg {
		transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-emphatic);
	}
	.solutions__link:hover {
		gap: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--accent-cool);
		border-color: var(--accent-cool);
	}
	.solutions__link:hover svg {
		transform: translateX(3px);
	}
	.solutions__divider {
		width: 1px;
		height: 1.4rem;
		background: #B8AE9E;
	}

	.solutions__glyph {
		position: absolute;
		top: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		right: clamp(1rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		width: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6rem);
		height: auto;
		color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--color-sienne) 35%, transparent);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.solutions__hairline {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: min(40rem, 70%);
		height: 1px;
		background: linear-gradient(
			to right,
			transparent,
			#B8AE9E 30%,
			#B8AE9E 70%,
			transparent
		);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.solutions__cta {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: flex-start;
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}
		.solutions__divider {
			display: none;
		}
	}
</style>
